  <spirit:description>
    6-Channel Triple Modular Redundancy (TMR) Majority-3 Voter.
    Implements bit-wise majority voting across three redundant core outputs.
    Uses Xilinx LUT3 primitives (INIT=8'hE8) for the Majority-3 function.
    Channels: ready (1b), boot_valid (1b), exit_valid (1b), exit_code (8b),
              print_valid (1b), print_data (32b). Total: 44x LUT3, 0 FF.
    Compatible with Xilinx 7-series, UltraScale, UltraScale+.
  </spirit:description>

